cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.SD

The paper discusses a reinforcement learning-based framework for learning to abstract sequential data in a goal-driven way. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions applications to sketch, video, and text data, indicating that it may also belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), and/or Sound (cs.SD) sub-categories.
